metadata.description:
I am loading this collection to try to help my city and my country. 
I am from Chernihiv and we feel, see and hear this war terrorism everyday, every minute. 
We have brave souls and inner power to be strong and believe in a peaceful future. We feel all the support from all over the world, and we are grateful for this!

This charity-sale will be divided on:
80% for food, equipment, local military stuff, petrol
10% for new mints

I am open to your messages, questions, cooperation!

After war.. I will be happy to send you a physically printed picture!
